===Verb===
'''bergen''' (''third-person singular simple present'' '''[[birgt]]''', ''[[past tense]]'' '''[[barg]]''', ''[[past participle]]'' '''[[geborgen]]''')

# to [[save]].
# to [[salvage]], [[rescue]].
# to [[conceal]], [[shelter]].

====Phrases====
